[SPEAKER_00] Tu smo svi i zajednice, i bogoslovi, i Stjepan, i svi ostali svećenici.

130
00:16:51,779 --> 00:16:56,100
[SPEAKER_00] Ako bilo ko ima kakav problem, pa tu smo, pitajte, bilo šta.

131
00:16:56,100 --> 00:17:04,119
[SPEAKER_00] Tako u nevezanoj komunikaciji ja sam razgovarao sa zvonetom.

132
00:17:05,539 --> 00:17:10,859
[SPEAKER_00] I meni je fasciniralo kada je on rekao da se on svako jutro pomali i kaže

133
00:17:10,859 --> 00:17:15,559
[SPEAKER_00] Bože, blagoslovi svaku osobu koju će danas sresti.

134
00:17:15,559 --> 00:17:18,240
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je to bilo prosvetljenje.

135
00:17:18,240 --> 00:17:19,880
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je to lijepo čut.

136
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:21,119
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je lijepo čut.

137
00:17:21,119 --> 00:17:25,160
[SPEAKER_00] Da za osobu koju ne poznaješ, koju samo vidiš i pogledaš,

138
00:17:25,160 --> 00:17:28,400
[SPEAKER_00] ti kažeš i moliš na nju, a to je meni predivno.

139
00:17:28,400 --> 00:17:29,720
[SPEAKER_00] Savršeno.

140
00:17:29,720 --> 00:17:32,559
[SPEAKER_00] Zahvala sam na njemu, na to me stvarno.

141
00:17:34,559 --> 00:17:38,400
[SPEAKER_00] I još bih samo nešto htio reći.

142
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:45,359
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, nakon svega toga što sam ja činio,

143
00:17:45,359 --> 00:17:47,759
[SPEAKER_00] koliko sam zaprljao svoju dušu.

144
00:17:47,759 --> 00:17:55,240
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, pogleda mi sada u bijeloj kalini.

145
00:17:59,559 --> 00:18:02,720
[SPEAKER_00] Bog mi je dao da budem s njim na altaru.

146
00:18:02,720 --> 00:18:05,859
[SPEAKER_00] Sa cijelim nebom.

147
00:18:09,180 --> 00:18:10,500
[SPEAKER_00] da tako sam prljao bio.

148
00:18:10,500 --> 00:18:13,019
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko nas Bog ljubi.

149
00:18:13,019 --> 00:18:16,720
[SPEAKER_00] Zato želim svima

150
00:18:16,720 --> 00:18:19,980
[SPEAKER_00] da osjetite koliko nas Bog ljubi.

151
00:18:19,980 --> 00:18:22,200
[SPEAKER_00] Sve nas.

152
00:18:25,579 --> 00:18:27,619
[SPEAKER_00] Samo da mu pružimo ruku, jer samo to traži.

153
00:18:27,619 --> 00:18:31,160
[SPEAKER_00] Da mu dođemo i kažemo evo ne.

154
00:18:35,160 --> 00:18:41,119
[SPEAKER_00] Duše sve ti na poj srce povjere.

155
00:18:41,119 --> 00:18:45,579
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje god zoveš taj da krene.

156
00:18:45,579 --> 00:18:50,779
[SPEAKER_00] Po morima da hodam.

157
00:18:51,779 --> 00:18:53,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ti me volim.

158
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:57,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ti gdje su največe dubine.

159
00:18:57,259 --> 00:19:01,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ti živi, drugi sine.

160
00:19:01,039 --> 00:19:05,700
[SPEAKER_00] Znam da spasim te ne ovdje.

